name: Purple Crackle Effect
description:
Purple and Black Metallic Crackle Effect
Simple yet effective, perfect for a night out.

Metallic-look Patterned Nail Wraps - these are THE nail care treatment this year because they are so easy to use. NO SMUDGING. NO CHIPPING. NO DRYING TIME. Get a professional result within minutes.

These nails allow a shiny, textured, full gloss nail colour effect for up to 9 days, meaning they are the perfect alternative to nail varnish/false nails.

A pack contains 16 nail foils for your nails and/ or toes and can be applied within 10 minutes.
